      "writtenOn": "2020-06-22T13:46:43Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This goes against the entire point of the original, which was to avoid as much work as possible, especially in the common case. This code basically enforces the super slow path every time.",
      "revId": "b3833f72eacacc70e8b17afd59c591633869c981",
